children.demo: Your parcel has been packed and ready to be handed over to our shipping provider.

requestCodes.code:
client = LazopApiClient::Client.new(url, appkey, appSecret)
request = LazopApiClient::Request.new('/logistic/order/trace')
request.add_api_parameter("order_id", "56150613585762")
request.add_api_parameter("locale", "en")
request.add_api_parameter("ofcPackageIdList", "[]")
response = client.execute(request, accessToken)
puts response.success?
puts response.body

client = lazop.LazopClient(url, appkey ,appSecret)
request = lazop.LazopRequest('/logistic/order/trace')
request.add_api_param('order_id', '56150613585762')
request.add_api_param('locale', 'en')
request.add_api_param('ofcPackageIdList', '[]')
response = client.execute(request, access_token)
print(response.type)
print(response.body)
